{"type":"message","id":"3b63c3a7","parentId":"5fab3e3f","timestamp":"2026-03-25T05:48:25.948Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在需要更新Program.cs，确保HTTPS重定向在生产环境启用。当前代码已经有`app.UseHttpsRedirection()`，我需要修改它，使其只在生产环境启用。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_720f78a17896459e9588ea2c","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"/root/.openclaw/tang-sansheng/projects/tianyou-platform/backend/src/Tianyou.Api/Program.cs","oldText":"// 开发环境启用Swagger\nif (app.Environment.IsDevelopment())\n{\n    app.UseSwagger();\n    app.UseSwaggerUI(c =>\n    {\n        c.SwaggerEndpoint(\"/swagger/v1/swagger.json\", \"Tianyou API v1\");\n        c.RoutePrefix = \"swagger\";\n    });\n}\n\napp.UseHttpsRedirection();","newText":"// 开发环境启用Swagger\nif (app.Environment.IsDevelopment())\n{\n    app.UseSwagger();\n    app.UseSwaggerUI(c =>\n    {\n        c.SwaggerEndpoint(\"/swagger/v1/swagger.json\", \"Tianyou API v1\");\n        c.RoutePrefix = \"swagger\";\n    });\n}\nelse\n{\n    // 生产环境强制HTTPS重定向\n    app.UseHttpsRedirection();\n}"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":254,"output":231,"cacheRead":16576,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":17061,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774417698549}}
