{"type":"message","id":"89912c98","parentId":"9cf6cfe7","timestamp":"2026-03-25T05:48:42.421Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_f58f17c4610942bf88bfb1b0","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"/root/.openclaw/tang-sansheng/projects/tianyou-platform/frontend/Tianyou.Web/Pages/UserManagement.razor\n/root/.openclaw/tang-sansheng/projects/tianyou-platform/frontend/Tianyou.Web/Pages/EntityList.razor"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":30,"aggregated":"/root/.openclaw/tang-sansheng/projects/tianyou-platform/frontend/Tianyou.Web/Pages/UserManagement.razor\n/root/.openclaw/tang-sansheng/projects/tianyou-platform/frontend/Tianyou.Web/Pages/EntityList.razor","cwd":"/root/.openclaw/tang-sansheng/workspace-bingbu"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774417722412}}
{"type":"message","id":"ca3402c4","parentId":"89912c98","timestamp":"2026-03-25T05:48:46.246Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"找到了文件，让我读取它们。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_4513ecfdea6449a9a886373d","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/root/.openclaw/tang-sansheng/projects/tianyou-platform/frontend/Tianyou.Web/Pages/UserManagement.razor"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_58561f343a0e4e7b978ddc33","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/root/.openclaw/tang-sansheng/projects/tianyou-platform/frontend/Tianyou.Web/Pages/EntityList.razor"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":164,"output":82,"cacheRead":17536,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":17782,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774417722422}}
{"type":"message","id":"866fdb7b","parentId":"ca3402c4","timestamp":"2026-03-25T05:48:46.291Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_4513ecfdea6449a9a886373d","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"@page \"/users\"\n@using Microsoft.AspNetCore.Authorization\n@using System.Net.Http.Json\n@using System.Net.Http.Headers\n@using Tianyou.Web.Services\n@attribute [Authorize]\n@inject HttpClient Http\n@inject NavigationManager NavManager\n@inject AuthService AuthService\n\n<h3>👥 用户管理</h3>\n\n<div class=\"mb-3\">\n    <button class=\"btn btn-primary\" @onclick=\"CreateUser\">➕ 新增用户</button>\n    <button class=\"btn btn-secondary\" @onclick=\"LoadUsers\">🔄 刷新</button>\n</div>\n\n@if (loading)\n{\n    <div class=\"text-center\">\n        <div class=\"spinner-border\" role=\"status\">\n            <span class=\"visually-hidden\">加载中...</span>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n}\nelse if (users == null || users.Count == 0)\n{\n    <div class=\"alert alert-info\">暂无用户数据</div>\n}\nelse\n{\n    <div class=\"table-responsive\">\n        <table class=\"table table-striped table-hover\">\n            <thead class=\"table-dark\">\n                <tr>\n                    <th>用户名</th>\n                    <th>邮箱</th>\n                    <th>角色</th>\n                    <th>状态</th>\n                    <th>创建时间</th>\n                    <th>操作</th>\n                </tr>\n            </thead>\n            <tbody>\n                @foreach (var user in users)\n                {\n                    <tr>\n                        <td><strong>@user.Username</strong></td>\n                        <td>@user.Email</td>\n                        <td><span class=\"badge bg-primary\">@user.Role</span></td>\n                        <td>\n                            <span class=\"badge @(user.IsActive ? \"bg-success\" : \"bg-secondary\")\">\n                                @(user.IsActive ? \"激活\" : \"禁用\")\n                            </span>\n                        </td>\n                        <td>@user.CreatedAt.ToString(\"yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm\")</td>\n                        <td>\n                            <button class=\"btn btn-sm btn-warning\" @onclick=\"() => EditUser(user.UserId)\">编辑</button>\n                            <button class=\"btn btn-sm btn-danger\" @onclick=\"() => DeleteUser(user.UserId)\">删除</button>\n                        </td>\n                    </tr>\n                }\n            </tbody>\n        </table>\n    </div>\n}\n\n@code {\n    private List<UserDto> users = new();\n    private bool loading = true;\n\n    protected override async Task OnInitializedAsync()\n    {\n        await LoadUsers();\n    }\n\n    private async Task LoadUsers()\n    {\n        loading = true;\n        try\n        {\n            // 获取Token\n            var token = await AuthService.GetTokenAsync();\n            \n            if (string.IsNullOrEmpty(token))\n            {\n                // 没有Token，跳转到登录页\n                Console.WriteLine(\"未登录，跳转到登录页\");\n                NavManager.NavigateTo(\"/login\");\n                return;\n            }\n            \n            // 创建带Authorization header的HttpClient\n            using var requestMessage = new HttpRequestMessage(HttpMethod.Get, \n                \"http://192.168.50.251:8091/api/users?page=1&size=10\");\n            requestMessage.Headers.Authorization = new AuthenticationHeaderValue(\"Bearer\", token);\n            \n            var response = await Http.SendAsync(requestMessage);\n            \n            if (response.IsSuccessStatusCode)\n            {\n                var content = await response.Content.ReadAsStringAsync();\n                var apiResponse = System.Text.Json.JsonSerializer.Deserialize<ApiResponse<UserListData>>(content, \n                    new System.Text.Json.JsonSerializerOptions \n                    { \n                        PropertyNamingPolicy = System.Text.Json.JsonNamingPolicy.CamelCase \n                    });\n                \n                if (apiResponse != null && apiResponse.Success && apiResponse.Data != null)\n                {\n                    users = apiResponse.Data.Users.Select(u => new UserDto\n                    {\n                        UserId = u.UserId,\n                        Username = u.Username,\n                        Email = u.Email,\n                        Role = u.Roles != null && u.Roles.Count > 0 ? u.Roles[0] : \"普通用户\",\n                        IsActive = u.IsActive,\n                        CreatedAt = u.CreatedAt\n                    }).ToList();\n                    \n                    StateHasChanged();\n                }\n                else\n                {\n                    Console.WriteLine($\"加载用户失败: API返回失败\");\n                    users = new List<UserDto>();\n                }\n            }\n            else if (response.StatusCode == System.Net.HttpStatusCode.Unauthorized)\n            {\n                // Token过期，跳转到登录页\n                Console.WriteLine(\"Token过期，请重新登录\");\n                NavManager.NavigateTo(\"/login\");\n                return;\n            }\n            else\n            {\n                Console.WriteLine($\"加载用户失败: HTTP {(int)response.StatusCode}\");\n                users = new List<UserDto>();\n            }\n        }\n        catch (Exception ex)\n        {\n            Console.WriteLine($\"加载失败: {ex.Message}\");\n            users = new List<UserDto>();\n        }\n        loading = false;\n    }\n\n    private void CreateUser()\n    {\n        NavManager.NavigateTo(\"/users/create\");\n    }\n\n    private void EditUser(Guid userId)\n    {\n        NavManager.NavigateTo($\"/users/{userId}/edit\");\n    }\n\n    private async Task DeleteUser(Guid userId)\n    {\n        users.RemoveAll(u => u.UserId == userId);\n        StateHasChanged();\n    }\n\n    // DTO类\n    public class UserDto\n    {\n        public Guid UserId { get; set; }\n        public string Username { get; set; } = \"\";\n        public string Email { get; set; } = \"\";\n        public string Role { get; set; } = \"\";\n        public bool IsActive { get; set; }\n        public DateTime CreatedAt { get; set; }\n    }\n\n    // API响应类\n    public class ApiResponse<T>\n    {\n        public bool Success { get; set; }\n        public T Data { get; set; }\n    }\n\n    public class UserListData\n    {\n        public List<UserData> Users { get; set; }\n        public int Total { get; set; }\n        public int Page { get; set; }\n        public int Size { get; set; }\n    }\n\n    public class UserData\n    {\n        public Guid UserId { get; set; }\n        public string Username { get; set; }\n        public string Email { get; set; }\n        public List<string> Roles { get; set; }\n        public bool IsActive { get; set; }\n        public DateTime CreatedAt { get; set; }\n    }\n}\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774417726285}}
{"type":"message","id":"69e781f2","parentId":"866fdb7b","timestamp":"2026-03-25T05:48:46.298Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_58561f343a0e4e7b978ddc33","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"@page \"/entities\"\n@using Microsoft.AspNetCore.Authorization\n@attribute [Authorize]\n@inject HttpClient Http\n@inject NavigationManager NavManager\n\n<h3>📊 实体管理</h3>\n\n<div class=\"mb-3\">\n    <button class=\"btn btn-primary\" @onclick=\"CreateEntity\">➕ 创建实体</button>\n    <button class=\"btn btn-secondary\" @onclick=\"LoadEntities\">🔄 刷新</button>\n</div>\n\n@if (loading)\n{\n    <div class=\"text-center\">\n        <div class=\"spinner-border\" role=\"status\">\n            <span class=\"visually-hidden\">加载中...</span>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n}\nelse if (entities == null || entities.Count == 0)\n{\n    <div class=\"alert alert-info\">\n        暂无实体数据，请点击\"创建实体\"按钮添加\n    </div>\n}\nelse\n{\n    <div class=\"table-responsive\">\n        <table class=\"table table-striped table-hover\">\n            <thead class=\"table-dark\">\n                <tr>\n                    <th>实体名称</th>\n                    <th>表名</th>\n                    <th>描述</th>\n                    <th>字段数</th>\n                    <th>创建时间</th>\n                    <th>操作</th>\n                </tr>\n            </thead>\n            <tbody>\n                @foreach (var entity in entities)\n                {\n                    <tr>\n                        <td><strong>@entity.EntityName</strong></td>\n                        <td><code>@entity.TableName</code></td>\n                        <td>@entity.Description</td>\n                        <td><span class=\"badge bg-info\">@entity.FieldCount</span></td>\n                        <td>@entity.CreatedAt.ToString(\"yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm\")</td>\n                        <td>\n                            <button class=\"btn btn-sm btn-info\" @onclick=\"() => ViewDetail(entity.EntityId)\">查看</button>\n                            <button class=\"btn btn-sm btn-success\" @onclick=\"() => ManageData(entity.EntityId)\">数据</button>\n                        </td>\n                    </tr>\n                }\n            </tbody>\n        </table>\n    </div>\n}\n\n@code {\n    private List<EntityDto> entities = new();\n    private bool loading = true;\n\n    protected override async Task OnInitializedAsync()\n    {\n        await LoadEntities();\n    }\n\n    private async Task LoadEntities()\n    {\n        loading = true;\n        try\n        {\n            var response = await Http.GetFromJsonAsync<ApiResponse<List<EntityDto>>>(\"api/entities\");\n            if (response?.Success == true)\n            {\n                entities = response.Data;\n            }\n        }\n        catch (Exception ex)\n        {\n            Console.WriteLine($\"加载失败: {ex.Message}\");\n        }\n        loading = false;\n    }\n\n    private void CreateEntity()\n    {\n        NavManager.NavigateTo(\"/entities/create\");\n    }\n\n    private void ViewDetail(Guid entityId)\n    {\n        NavManager.NavigateTo($\"/entities/{entityId}\");\n    }\n\n    private void ManageData(Guid entityId)\n    {\n        NavManager.NavigateTo($\"/entities/{entityId}/data\");\n    }\n\n    public class EntityDto\n    {\n        public Guid EntityId { get; set; }\n        public string EntityName { get; set; } = \"\";\n        public string TableName { get; set; } = \"\";\n        public string? Description { get; set; }\n        public int FieldCount { get; set; }\n        public DateTime CreatedAt { get; set; }\n    }\n\n    public class ApiResponse<T>\n    {\n        public bool Success { get; set; }\n        public T? Data { get; set; }\n        public string? Message { get; set; }\n    }\n}"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774417726291}}
{"type":"message","id":"cc7eaefe","parentId":"69e781f2","timestamp":"2026-03-25T05:48:54.546Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，我已经读取了两个文件。现在需要添加删除确认机制。\n\n**UserManagement.razor**:\n- 有删除按钮，但没有确认对话框\n- 需要添加确认对话框\n\n**EntityList.razor**:\n- 没有删除按钮，需要添加\n- 也需要添加确认对话框\n\n让我先修改UserManagement.razor，添加删除确认对话框。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_7ba3bb0140ce44ec84466201","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"/root/.openclaw/tang-sansheng/projects/tianyou-platform/frontend/Tianyou.Web/Pages/UserManagement.razor","oldText":"                        <td>\n                            <button class=\"btn btn-sm btn-warning\" @onclick=\"() => EditUser(user.UserId)\">编辑</button>\n                            <button class=\"btn btn-sm btn-danger\" @onclick=\"() => DeleteUser(user.UserId)\">删除</button>\n                        </td>","newText":"                        <td>\n                            <button class=\"btn btn-sm btn-warning\" @onclick=\"() => EditUser(user.UserId)\">编辑</button>\n                            <button class=\"btn btn-sm btn-danger\" @onclick=\"() => ConfirmDeleteUser(user.UserId, user.Username)\">删除</button>\n                        </td>"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":2214,"output":251,"cacheRead":17664,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":20129,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774417726298}}
